title: The Scuttling Swarm
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

For every Brood of Gaunts of 30 models included in a detachment, you can include one ''Tervigon'' as though it were a Dedicated Transport for that unit, except the unit //cannot// start the game embarked on the ''Tervigon'' and the ''Tervigon'' //does// occupy a Force Organization slot (the same as that of the chosen unit, not an ''HQ'' choice). These Tervigons possess the ''Spawn Gaunts'' special rule instead of the ''Spawn Termagants'' special rule. See the additional Army List entries for the ''Tervigon'' under ''Troops'' and ''Fast Attack'' for more information.